Package de.gematik.bbriccs.crypto.certificate

Enum Class ProfessionOid

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ProfessionOid>
de.gematik.bbriccs.crypto.certificate.ProfessionOid
All Implemented Interfaces:
Oid, Serializable, Comparable<ProfessionOid>, Constable
public enum ProfessionOid extends Enum<ProfessionOid> implements Oid
This enum contains the OIDs for the professions used in the gematik ecosystem. The OIDs are used to identify the profession of a healthcare professional in certificates.
